                                    <font key="font" metaFont="message" size="11"/>
                                    <string key="title">The application uses macOS's standard tagging mechanism. Please ensure that the tag names and colors in this app exactly match those in Finder; otherwise, you may encounter inconsistencies in tag colors when displaying or writing tags.</string>
