                                <textFieldCell key="cell" selectable="YES" id="6PU-he-9gg">
                                    <font key="font" metaFont="message" size="11"/>
                                    <string key="title">Because macOS Spotlight cannot index external disks, network drives, or the contents of directories excluded in the "Search Privacy" settings, this app introduces an enhanced indexing feature: when you browse a folder within the app, it records the tags associated with the files inside that folder.

Later, when you select the corresponding tag in the directory tree, the app will supplement the system's search results by displaying the relevant files.</string>
